94
00:03:38,496 --> 00:03:39,737
you can still go like, okay, well,

95
00:03:39,737 --> 00:03:41,017
it's just a couple of people, I can handle that.

96
00:03:41,017 --> 00:03:44,139
But the team grows because that's what you got hired to.

97
00:03:44,139 --> 00:03:46,861
So over time, the team went to about 50 people

98
00:03:46,861 --> 00:03:49,382
and team meetings became a monster

99
00:03:49,382 --> 00:03:51,804
because you're standing in front of 50 people,

100
00:03:51,804 --> 00:03:53,485
they're waiting you and expecting you

101
00:03:53,485 --> 00:03:54,305
to know what you're doing,

102
00:03:54,305 --> 00:03:55,626
but you have no clue what's going on.

103
00:03:56,926 --> 00:04:01,247
