104
00:04:01,247 --> 00:04:04,968
we do like the first team meeting, and I'm scared as hell because

105
00:04:04,968 --> 00:04:06,708
they expect me to know what's going on and I'm like, hi.

106
00:04:06,708 --> 00:04:11,509
And that's pretty much the monster that's chasing you. So like your imposter

107
00:04:11,509 --> 00:04:15,030
syndrome gets worse because there's this thing that you're

108
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:17,510
running away from because you don't want to make them know that you're an

109
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:21,511
imposter. And then things get worse because...

110
00:04:22,674 --> 00:04:25,015
now that you move into direction,

111
00:04:25,015 --> 00:04:26,956
you get information that is exclusive to you.

112
00:04:26,956 --> 00:04:29,877
So you know schedules, you know all the problems,

113
00:04:29,877 --> 00:04:31,458
you know like politics way more

114
00:04:31,458 --> 00:04:33,239
that are usually being kept away from you.

115
00:04:33,239 --> 00:04:34,699
You get to know like all the details

116
00:04:34,699 --> 00:04:37,901
that make the problems seem even more impossible.

117
00:04:38,681 --> 00:04:41,802
And so that small foundation that you work so hard on,

118
00:04:41,802 --> 00:04:43,882
that you feel like, oh, I'm the artist, I can handle this.

119
00:04:43,882 --> 00:04:49,103
It's crumbling because all that stuff that you have

120
00:04:49,103 --> 00:04:51,724
is not, wait, no way that's gonna work out, like ever.

121
00:04:51,724 --> 00:04:54,064
Because it just makes everything crumble at that point.

122
00:04:54,064 --> 00:04:56,004
So I got nervous, I was super nervous.

123
00:04:56,004 --> 00:04:58,025
I couldn't talk to people, I got anxious.

124
00:04:58,025 --> 00:04:59,725
I'm a weird personality in general,

