129
00:05:09,547 --> 00:05:12,449
I need to change something because I can't be that nervous,

130
00:05:12,449 --> 00:05:13,891
insecure person in front of my team.

131
00:05:13,891 --> 00:05:16,033
It will just, won't work.

132
