136
00:05:27,902 --> 00:05:29,543
When we were doing board game nights,

137
00:05:29,543 --> 00:05:30,284
at some point I caught it up.

138
00:05:30,284 --> 00:05:32,345
Like I went through iteration like a proper game developer.

139
00:05:32,345 --> 00:05:33,126
I thought that one's good.

140
